creator: Voice app
descriptionHtml:
List of Yandex Alisa voice commands. All commands are categorised.

This is the reference app and it doesn't contain the Alisa virtual assistant. You can use those commands to control music, getting routes and addresses, getting facts and other functions in the apps called "Yandex" and "Yandex Browser".

This app was not created or endorsed by Yandex.
descriptionShort: List of virtual assistant Yandex Alice voice commands.
